  <!-- SECTION 5: WHY LAST COIN STANDING -->
  <section class="about-section closing-section">
    <div class="section-label">Why "Last Coin Standing"?</div>
    <p>Bitcoin may be the most consequential development since the printing press - a once-in-civilization opportunity to advance human prosperity in a way nothing else can. I write about it, build tools around it, and work on it full-time because I believe its destiny is to become the last coin standing.</p>
